                | Datica Platform Subscription
              p A Datica Platform subscription is comprised of a <em>Licensing</em> and a <em>Continuous Compliance Management</em> Fee.
              h4.headline-5 
                = inline_svg("small/icon-ui-checkmark", class: "icon-inline icon-left svg-color--green") 
