              p We can deploy a Kubernetes cluster into your cloud account, or Datica's cloud. We give you the flexibility to decide how much, or how little you want to manage.
              h4.headline-5 
                = inline_svg("small/icon-ui-checkmark", class: "icon-inline icon-left svg-color--green") 
                | Support
              p All customers receive basic ticket support with their Platform subscription. We also offer premium support to enterprise customers.
              h4.headline-5 
                = inline_svg("small/icon-plus-circle", class: "icon-inline icon-left svg-color--blue")
