                | Add-ons
              p We're dedicated to giving you the flexibility you need, while still providing the highest level of compliance available on the market. With add-ons, Datica can make any cloud native service compliant. Additionally, our industry-leading approach to EHR integration includes an HA Mirth Connect Environment.
              h4.headline-5 
